ense\n\n### Sentence Length\n\n<br>\n<div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n## Missing Data\n\nThis section will have information about missing parole eligibility data for the state once new NCRP data is released.\n\n\n\n\n\n# Prison Population\n\nThe size and composition of the prison population have significant implications for state resources and public safety. \n\nSentence about change in year-end population from 2010 to 2020.  \nTrend graph\n\n<br>\n<div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n## Demographics\n\nAn examination of the demographic composition of Georgia's prison population, including age, gender, race, and other relevant factors.  \n\n<br>\n<div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n## Criminal Offenses\n\nAn overview of the types of criminal offenses that lead to incarceration, providing insight into the most common crimes and their prevalence.  \n\n<br>\n<div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n## Sentence Lengths\n\nAnalysis of the distribution of sentence lengths within the prison population.  \n\n\n# Prison Releases\n\nUnderstanding trends in prison releases is crucial for assessing the effectiveness of parole and reentry programs.  \n\nSentence about change in releases from 2010 to 2020.\nTrend graph\n\n## Prison Release Types\n\n<br>\n<div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n## Demographics\n\nA demographic analysis of individuals released from prison, highlighting trends and patterns in reentry.  \n\n<br>\n<div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n## Timing of Release\n\nAn exploration of the timing of prison releases, including how long individuals serve before being released.  \n\n<br>\n<div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n## Time Served by Offense Type\n\nDetailed analysis of the average time served by individuals based on their offense type, providing insights into sentencing practices and their outcomes.  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n# Disparities\n\nExamining disparities within the prison system is essential for addressing issues of equity and justice. This section focuses on disparities in incarceration and release practices.  \n\nIn prison.\n\n## In Prison Past Their Parole Eligibility Date\n\n<br>\n<div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n## Timing of Release\n\n<br>\n<div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n## Timing of Release by Offense Type\n\n<br>\n<div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n## Time Served \n\n<br>\n<div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n:::\n\n</div>\n\n\n---\ntitle: \"Georgia\"\n---\n",
